@baseUrl = http://localhost:5050
@bearerToken = <paste_jwt_from_auth0_here>

### Sync Auth0 user to local DB (call after Auth0 login)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/public/auth/sync
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### Get current authenticated user profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/public/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
